    "So, maximizing the hydrogen storage capacity can be facilitated using the proposed models.",
    "It should be mentioned that one of the research's issues is the established models are restricted to AB 2 metal hydrides.",
    "Therefore, the foregoing models may encounter shortcomings in the other types of metal hydrate.",
    "Accordingly, generating models based on more extensive types of metal hydrate could be another line of future investigation.",
    "The prediction of hydrogen storage capacity in the AB 2 metal hydrides was argued in the present study developing three machine learning algorithms including GA-LSSVM, PSO-LSSVM, and HGAPSO-LSSVM."
